{"tid":1744590,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"淡化中國製造2025》中國發改委新政策 曝製造業強權野心","createTime":"2019-11-21T22:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T03:59:54.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ae6118a8b962619f047d7eefea505d8ae43d4e25","tid":1744590,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T22:51:51.000Z","msg":"淡化中國製造2025》中國發改委新政策 曝製造業強權野心<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/paper/1332429\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fpaper%2F1332429&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt84MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=b8db1ba0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fpaper%2F1332429&h=cadbcf1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/paper/1332429</a><br />\n<br />\n〔編譯魏國金／綜合報導〕中國當局二○一五年提出「中國製造二○二五」計畫，全面推展製造業強國戰略；該計畫成為美中貿易衝突的主要議題之一後，中國加以淡化。不過，中國十五日宣布新政策，目標在二○二五年形成一批旗艦企業、平台，以及示範區，以推動先進製造業發展，顯示中國並未放棄成為全球製造業強權的野心。<br />\n<br />\n2025年建立旗艦企業、平台、示範區<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》報導，中國國家發展和改革委員會等十五個政府部門制定一套新政策，以增強製造業核心競爭力並且培植現代產業體系；相關計畫強調先進技術的使用，例如人工智慧以及新一代資訊技術在製造業與服務業中的應用，涵蓋汽車與先進設備等一系列的工業部門。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，發改委公布上述聲明，正值美國與中國致力達成貿易協議之際；五年前中國推出「中國製造二○二五」政策，引發美國川普政府批評該計畫鼓勵國家補貼本國企業、強迫外企技術轉讓，是對公平競爭的威脅，相關指控也成為美國對中國發動貿易戰與關稅戰的理據。<br />\n<br />\n儘管北京為緩和與美關係的緊張，對該計畫轉趨低調，但在此之前，中國大加宣揚「中國製造二○二五」，視其為實現製造業強國的戰略目標。英國布魯奈爾大學經濟系教授劉芍佳曾表示，該政策與中國國家主席習近平提出的「中國夢」政治理念一致。"},{"pid":"1527bb59f72847e461239d3e06082f250f400742","tid":1744590,"uid":178364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T22:55:11.000Z","msg":"改個名又再上場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f155b24ffd05c37f80ec9e771357b87f560ef4","tid":1744590,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T23:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce04c7b0a0c73989961c393dcca03fbed845b921","tid":1744590,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T01:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0371bba0ee6c8b054ba59da6a85023d4d5ac535","tid":1744590,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T01:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要落力偷多啲"},{"pid":"158c2426d4e8324999c83e8d9ef08fc70222a239","tid":1744590,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95124af29aa8a443a5ad53d4f09755a3cfcac4d","tid":1744590,"uid":16109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:59:54.000Z","msg":"新四大發明去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}